{"tid":649097,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【紗布封喉亡】聆訊前一周突延期　家屬嘆已等了近7年：無咩辦法","createTime":"2018-05-01T09:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T13:04:27.000Z","uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2515e9c3a9b952a9043892b1f33349a70c7cd1ce","tid":649097,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T09:03:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/178282/%E7%B4%97%E5%B8%83%E5%B0%81%E5%96%89%E4%BA%A1-%E8%81%86%E8%A8%8A%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E7%AA%81%E5%BB%B6%E6%9C%9F-%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E5%98%86%E5%B7%B2%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%86%E8%BF%917%E5%B9%B4-%E7%84%A1%E5%92%A9%E8%BE%A6%E6%B3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F178282%2F%25E7%25B4%2597%25E5%25B8%2583%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%2596%2589%25E4%25BA%25A1-%25E8%2581%2586%25E8%25A8%258A%25E5%2589%258D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2591%25A8%25E7%25AA%2581%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E6%259C%259F-%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E5%2598%2586%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E7%25AD%2589%25E4%25BA%2586%25E8%25BF%25917%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2592%25A9%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E6%25B3%2595&d=gCz%2Bn9pUQ%2BW1BqbAcjAdyQKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=82b66f47\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/178282/%E7%B4%97%E5%B8%83%E5%B0%81%E5%96%89%E4%BA%A1-%E8%81%86%E8%A8%8A%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E7%AA%81%E5%BB%B6%E6%9C%9F-%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E5%98%86%E5%B7%B2%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%86%E8%BF%917%E5%B9%B4-%E7%84%A1%E5%92%A9%E8%BE%A6%E6%B3%95</a><br />\n<br />\n轟動一時的「紗布封喉」醫療事故，死者兒子王冰蕓苦候近7年，原本醫務委員會訂於今日（4月16日）召開紀律聆訊。<br />\n不過至開庭前4天，醫委會突然決定聆訊延期，但無交代原因。<br />\n王冰蕓亦獲知聆訊需要延期，暫未知延至何時舉行。他對聆訊需改期大感無奈，但直言「無咩辦法」。<br />\n<br />\n記者上一次與王冰蕓面對面訪談，已是4月初的事，記者問他對於首度聆訊的期望，他淡然地說「一半一半啦，好多嘢唔係自己控制到」，豈料這句竟一語成讖。<br />\n「紗布封喉」事故發生於2011年，王冰蕓的父親王肯構咽喉的永久造口，疑因被九龍醫院的醫護人員以紗布封實致死，王冰蕓翌年向醫委會投訴涉事醫生，事故發生至今近7年，王冰蕓終於等到一個聆訊的機會，醫委會原訂定於今年4月16日及17日聆訊，他受訪時直言自己所能做到的是將個案「擺上枱」，讓大家知道事故因由。<br />\n醫務委員會秘書處今日(16日)回覆《香港01》，醫委會主席於4月12日決定將原定4月16日及17日舉行的紀律研訊延期。由於醫委會具行使紀律處分的權力，故不適宜就個別醫生的紀律個案作出評論。 王冰蕓亦指，醫委會沒有向他正式交代研訊延期的原因。<br />\n醫委會曾以有新證據為由撤回聆訊<br />\n紀律研訊除了有可能突然改期，醫委會在聆訊前突然撤回聆訊亦曾經發生。另一投訴人黃先生的妻子疑因醫生處方藥物不當，於2013年離世，黃先生同年向醫委會投訴，個案一度獲排期於2016年聆訊，惟醫委會於聆訊前兩個月，突然以「辯方律師提交新資料顯示不應偵訊」撤回聆訊，他其後作出第二次投訴，暫未有進展。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1365309/org/dcd2c66bcc5213a149c7e89dc1ced9a2.png/PSHY3s-gWt7Lkrp2n4KsMaeG1ESijgiuOZOtuTmTrbk?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1365309%2Forg%2Fdcd2c66bcc5213a149c7e89dc1ced9a2.png%2FPSHY3s-gWt7Lkrp2n4KsMaeG1ESijgiuOZOtuTmTrbk%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=e0b1a1e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n封喉嗰D護士應該已經釘完牌返番去做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414b8f2f376b4a78a60a806dec6d1e5aea212938","tid":649097,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T09:04:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛賈雨村抹黑本土派有功<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/132845_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F132845_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=211da708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/132849_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F132849_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=1ad97502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/132859_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F132859_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=bbe0f1ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來大陸仔嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"ht